EN: I have a very good friend in a foreign country.

ZH: 他是我最好的朋友之一。
EN: He is one of my best friends.

ZH: 我的朋友们都很喜欢打篮球。
EN: My friends all like to play basketball.

ZH: 我和我的朋友们一起去爬山。
EN: I go mountain climbing with my friends.

ZH: 我的朋友们总是支持我。
EN: My friends always support me.

ZH: 我的朋友喜欢和我一起看电影。
EN: My friend likes to watch movies with me.

ZH: 我的朋友们都在外地读书。
EN: My friends are all studying abroad.

ZH: 我有一些朋友是老师。
EN: I have some friends who are teachers.

ZH: 我的朋友是非常值得信任的人。
EN: My friend is a very trustworthy person.

ZH: 我和朋友们一起度过了一个愉快的周末。
EN: I had a pleasant weekend with my friends.

ZH: 朋友之间要相互支持。
EN: Friends should support each other.

ZH: 我的朋友们都已经结婚了。
EN: My friends are all married.

ZH: 让我们的朋友圈更广阔。
EN: Let's expand our circle of friends.

ZH: 她是我多年的朋友。
EN: She is a friend I have known for many years.

ZH: 我的朋友很会做菜。
EN: My friend is very good at cooking.

